data.description: Welcome to this unique canal front residence, where your dream of waterfront living becomes a reality. This remarkable property offers direct canal frontage accompanied by a new vinyl seawall built in 2016.. Ideally situated near major highways, this home offers convenient access to Orlando, Port Canaveral, Cocoa Beach, and more. Nestled within a quiet and low-traffic neighborhood, this property provides a peaceful and secure environment that is perfect for unwinding and enjoying waterfront serenity. With numerous upgrades, including renovated interiors and dual air conditioners, this waterfront paradise is designed for low-maintenance luxury living. Schedule your private showing today! Welcome to this unique canal front residence, where your dream of waterfront living becomes a reality. This remarkable property offers direct canal frontage accompanied by a new vinyl seawall built in 2016, ensuring private and easy access to the water for all your boating endeavors. As you step inside, prepare to be captivated by the beautifully renovated interior. The kitchen is a culinary masterpiece, featuring stunning stone countertops, top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, three ovens, ample cabinet storage, and a spacious island that serves as a focal point. Perfect for entertaining, the open concept living and dining area seamlessly blends together, offering the space to comfortably host family & friends. A powder bathroom is conveniently positioned off the entry and at the base of stairs. On the first floor, primary bedroom awaits. The rolling barn door opens to transition into the en-suite offering two walk-in closets, a stand in shower with spa glass and dual sinks. Upstairs, the secondary bedrooms, loft, flex room and a bathroom provide ideal accommodation for visiting guests. This extraordinary property doesn't stop there. It also includes a climate-controlled flex room connected to the 4-car plus tandem garage, offering a versatile space for pursuing your hobbies and interests. The exterior features are equally remarkable: an updated dock with remote boat lift, a convenient generator hook up, and an irrigation system that keeps the zoysia lawn vibrant and lush. The exterior paint received a refreshing update in 2019, ensuring long-lasting quality and aesthetics. The garage transformation into a 4 car tandem, front load, with 8 foot garage doors was completed in 2016. Outside, revel in the convenience of a deeded boat ramp, shared with your immediate neighbor, along with a private 7000lb boat lift equipped with a twin motor lift system. For fishing enthusiasts, the canal offers abundant opportunities to catch bass, crappie, bream, and even bow fish for tilapia. The dedicated screened cleaning room on the dock ensures a hassle-free experience to prep your fresh catch. You'll also enjoy the unique privilege of viewing rocket launches from the privacy of your own homean experience that will surely leave you in awe. Ideally situated near major highways, this home offers convenient access to Orlando, Port Canaveral, Cocoa Beach, and more. Nestled within a quiet and low-traffic neighborhood, this property provides a peaceful and secure environment that is perfect for unwinding and enjoying waterfront serenity. With numerous upgrades, including renovated interiors and dual air conditioners, this waterfront paradise is designed for low-maintenance luxury living. Seller has Liberty Home Guard Total Home Warranty good through November 27th 2024. Schedule your private showing today!
